{"tid":482163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"日本專家：人類喺2000萬年之後將進化成一個波！","createTime":"2017-11-28T02:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T12:21:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4793a4790b5ee187d647ced3ef00d3262eb9c5bc","tid":482163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:07:53.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/g_d_r_g_n_m_e_k/status/934372343337512960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fg_d_r_g_n_m_e_k%2Fstatus%2F934372343337512960&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ulhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d4b26417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fg_d_r_g_n_m_e_k%2Fstatus%2F934372343337512960&h=147c13be\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/g_d_r_g_n_m_e_k/status/934372343337512960</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DPeOrqjVoAEgnwe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDPeOrqjVoAEgnwe.jpg&h=054cdac8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eec69603481e0cf8f4a3c677746e99c385693435","tid":482163,"uid":44523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:09:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c13e538f04a9767091a7739530b7e2c05bee1ce8","tid":482163,"uid":51521,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"信專家食得屎<br />\n我就選擇信漫畫家<br />\n2000萬年後一定將係身體機械化"},{"pid":"2fdf8b62cb139ae9a4bacf7c61572fe0e5b3c6a5","tid":482163,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"人類從很久之前一直進化，根據進化論，由 700 萬年前的猿人到 250 萬年前的原人到現在的人類，變化十分大。然而，大家想像到 2000 萬年後人類會變成怎麽樣嗎？<br />\n<br />\n近日，日本有電視節目就請來專家，分析人類繼續進化下去的情況。一跳就跳到 2000 萬年之後，比之前加起來的都要長。結果亦十分驚人，雖然不知道「專家」是根據什麽來得出這個結果，然而大家看到這個「新人類」都嚇了一跳。因爲，這是一個只有頭跟四肢的「人」，頭超大、手長、腳短、腳掌超長，簡直就像是異型。要知道我們習慣用「頭大無腦，腦大生草」來話人，如果大家都是這個樣子的話，相信就已經不適用了。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都認爲這個模樣超像《IQ 博士》中的綠色外星人笑彈大王。幸運的是，至少預想中的「新人類」並不是屁股長在頭上，只是頭部比較大而已。還有網民覺得這個「新人類」有點像《emoji 大冒險》的 emoji 公仔，甚至是 M &amp; M 的吉祥物，然而 它們看上去就可愛得多。所以，看來問題在於頭變大之後，五官卻維持一樣的大小。如果頭部跟五官一起變大，究竟會更可愛還是更恐怖呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DPeSU3uVwAAzJGv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDPeSU3uVwAAzJGv.jpg&h=02242a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957036/2%20千萬年後人類進化成一個球？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1957036%2F2%2520%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%A1%9E%E9%80%B2%E5%8C%96%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E7%90%83%EF%BC%9F&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ulhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=55d6bb02\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957036/2%20千萬年後人類進化成一個球？</a>"},{"pid":"0a30857e29497bf27c85dd5ab348017d51244ca3","tid":482163,"uid":15620,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/101148_1b309f268cd1c1e7d1eda207d228fadb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F101148_1b309f268cd1c1e7d1eda207d228fadb.jpg&h=ec11b039&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"773fba784c94f1aa8473293be58a9be06d241f13","tid":482163,"uid":139139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"港女唔使再驚無波"},{"pid":"771de5fec89b72dda64f9edccc7ced5295be2b4a","tid":482163,"uid":43116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/101300_b326a36a7df59e877586a2536dc95bc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F101300_b326a36a7df59e877586a2536dc95bc8.jpg&h=2bdfa20a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63bb30cedcec18bf0f884fddad377701b29c300b","tid":482163,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1